name: Give Me Jesus Sticker/Decal
description:
This 5.5X5.5 inch sticker is printed on durable, high opacity adhesive vinyl which makes it perfect for regular use. Can be used for Car Decals, Wall Art/Decal, Laptop/Ipad/Phone Decor, and so much more, as well as for covering other stickers or paint. The high-quality vinyl ensures there are no bubbles when applying.


• High opacity film that’s impossible to see through
• Fast and easy bubble-free application
• Durable vinyl, perfect for indoor use
• 95µ density

Don't forget to clean the surface before applying the sticker.
